OL,3,CArtist transforms dolls' house into
OL,4,Cart gallery for 'Open Houses' festival
OL,6,FA Brighton artist sick of the cost of
OL,7,Fhousing in her hometown has created a
OL,8,Funique and mobile exhibit for the
OL,9,FArtists Open Houses Festival in the
OL,10,Fcity this month.
OL,12,FFaced with high rents and some of the
OL,13,Fmost expensive house prices in the UK,
OL,14,FBryony Devitt decided to channel her
OL,15,Ffrustrations into an art project
OL,16,Fexploring the housing crisis.
OL,18,FHer portable Open House is a dolls'
OL,19,Fhouse on wheels - filled with custom-
OL,20,Fmade miniature artworks by local and
OL,21,Finternational artists.
