OL,6,FBryony said: "Seeing how the housing
OL,7,Fcrisis is impacting people of all ages
OL,8,Facross our community was really
OL,9,Fgetting me down.
OL,11,F"The Portable Open House is my
OL,12,Fresponse to those feelings,
OL,13,Fcelebrating creativity and not letting
OL,14,Fit keep me down.
OL,16,F"It has been a cathartic experience -
OL,17,Ftotal escapism but also a great way to
OL,18,Fget people involved and talking about
OL,19,Fthe issue.
