OL,6,F"I'd recommend getting on the property
OL,7,Fladder to anyone... You've got to
OL,8,Fstart small right?"
OL,10,FAccording to the latest figures from
OL,11,Fthe Office for National Statistics,
OL,12,Fthe average UK private rent increased
OL,13,Fby a record 9.2% in the last year.
OL,15,FThe average price paid by first-time
OL,16,Fbuyers in Brighton and Hove dropped by
OL,17,F5% - to just under #370,000.
