OL,6,FBut for some, prices remain utterly
OL,7,Fout of reach - with 35 people found
OL,8,Fsleeping rough on a single night in
OL,9,Fthe city in March, double what it was
OL,10,Fin the same month two years ago.
OL,12,FArt inspired by the homeless, raising
OL,13,Fmoney for the charity, is also going
OL,14,Fon display at another new Open Houses
OL,15,Fvenue - nearby Cardinal Newman School.
OL,17,FPupil's work is mixing with
OL,18,Fprofessional donations in a "community
OL,19,Fresponse" to the issue.
