OL,7,Fguest work from as far afield as
OL,8,FNorway and Chile.
OL,10,FHer exhibition will go on a tour
OL,11,Facross the city over the four weekends
OL,12,Fof May, including at the Spiegel
OL,13,FGarden, Preston Park, Fiveways, Hove,
OL,14,FSeven Dials, Hanover and Kemptown.
